text:
Heylo Mr Cow,
Oe……………. happy bday.
Bhai bahut saati movies reh gayi and hum graduate ho gaye. Han bahut negative approach hai meri😛. But yeah, summer 19 was prolly the best time in the campus. And obviously the following semesters tooo. Bhai humne koi movie nahi chodi. Koi khaane ka spot nahi choda(atleast campus mai) , koi acchi dish nahi chodi, heck, we even went to a temple too(but haan uske baad movie was must). Waise to I have a lot to say, but mai bolunga nahi. Because words mai fitting accuracy bahut low hogi. I’m so so glad it happened and also sad because you know why.
On the other note, Nainital is “ON”.
author: Akhilesh  Chauhan

Milte hain kabhi jaldi hi.
All the best!
